trans-unit.source: Sets the identity of the user for an ASP.NET application when Windows authentication is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Anger identitet för ett ASP.NET-program när Windows-autentisering är aktiverad.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: When the authentication <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A> is set to <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode>, the WindowsAuthenticationModule sets the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> to an <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object that represents the Windows identity supplied by IIS for the current request.
trans-unit.target: När autentiseringen <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A>anges till <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode>, WindowsAuthenticationModule anger den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>-egenskapen för aktuellt <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>till ett <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objekt som representerar den Windows-identiteten som tillhandahålls av IIS för den aktuella begäranden.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If IIS uses anonymous authentication, then the WindowsAuthenticationModule uses the identity returned by the <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Om IIS använder för anonym autentisering av WindowsAuthenticationModule och använder sedan den identitet som returneras av den <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WindowsAuthenticationModule exposes an <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate> event that enables you to provide a custom <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object for the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: WindowsAuthenticationModule visar en <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>händelse som kan du ange ett anpassat <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objekt för <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>egenskapen för aktuellt <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate> event is accessed by specifying a subroutine named **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>händelse nås genom att ange en subrutin med namnet **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** i filen Global.asax för ASP.NET-program.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > In IIS 7.0, using the WindowsAuthenticationModule class with the <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationModule> class is not supported.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > I IIS 7.0, med hjälp av klassen WindowsAuthenticationModule med den <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationModule>klass stöds inte.</xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: For more information about compatibility issues in Integrated mode, see [Moving an ASP.NET Application from IIS 6.0 to IIS 7.0](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om kompatibilitet i integrerat läge finns [flyttar ett ASP.NET-program från IIS 6.0 till IIS 7.0](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en instans av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is not intended to be called from application code.
trans-unit.target: Den här konstruktorn är inte avsedd att anropas från programkod.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET calls this constructor to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> class.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET anropar den här konstruktorn för att skapa en instans av <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>klassen.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: After calling the constructor, it calls the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Init%2A> method to initialize the new <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> object.
trans-unit.target: När du anropar konstruktorn, anropar den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Init%2A>metod för att initiera den nya <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>objektet.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Init%2A>

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the application authenticates the current request.
trans-unit.target: Inträffar när programmet autentiserar den aktuella begäranden.

trans-unit.source: The Authenticate event is raised during the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> event.
trans-unit.target: Autentisera händelsen uppstår under den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>händelse.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>

trans-unit.source: You can access the Authenticate event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> class by specifying a subroutine named **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Du kan komma åt autentisera händelsen för den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>klass genom att ange en subrutin med namnet **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** i filen Global.asax för ASP.NET-program.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs> object supplied to the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event to set the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> to a custom <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>egenskapen för den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs>objekt som angetts för den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** händelsen för att ange den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>egenskapen för aktuellt <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>till en anpassad <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A> property during the **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event, the Windows identity supplied by IIS is used as the identity for the current request.
trans-unit.target: Om du inte anger ett värde för den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>egenskapen under den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** händelse Windows identitet som tillhandahålls av IIS används som identitet för den aktuella begäranden.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: If IIS uses anonymous authentication, then the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A> property is set to the identity returned by the <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Om IIS använder anonym autentisering kommer <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A>egenskap är inställd på den identitet som returneras av den <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity.GetAnonymous%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationEventArgs.Identity%2A>

trans-unit.source: The **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event is raised only when the authentication <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A> is set to <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode> and the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> is an active HTTP module for the application.
trans-unit.target: Den **WindowsAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** händelsen aktiveras endast när autentiseringen <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A>anges till <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode>och <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>är en aktiva HTTP-modul för programmet.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationMode> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthenticationSection.Mode%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > In IIS 7.0 running in Integrated Mode, the Authenticate event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> is not raised when both the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> and the IIS `AnonymousAuthenticationModule` modules are enabled.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > I IIS 7.0 körs i integrerat läge, autentisera händelsen för den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>utlöses inte när båda ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>och IIS `AnonymousAuthenticationModule` moduler är aktiverade.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: In this scenario, to receive authentication notification, subscribe to the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> event of the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> instance.
trans-unit.target: I det här scenariot för att ta emot meddelande om authentication prenumerera på <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>händelsen för den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication>instans.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> </xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>

trans-unit.source: For more information about compatibility issues in Integrated modes, see [Moving an ASP.NET Application from IIS 6.0 to IIS 7.0](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om problem med programkompatibilitet i integrerat läge finns [flyttar ett ASP.NET-program från IIS 6.0 till IIS 7.0](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources, other than memory, used by the <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigör alla resurser, förutom minne som används av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method is not intended to be called from application code.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden ska inte anropas från programkod.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Initierar den <xref href="System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: This method is not intended to be called from application code.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden ska inte anropas från programkod.

trans-unit.source: The Init method ensures that the <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule> is included in the processing of the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> event.
trans-unit.target: Init-metoden garanterar att den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>ingår i bearbetningen av den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>händelse.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> </xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: The current <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Aktuellt <xref href="System.Web.HttpApplication"> </xref> instans.
